**Authors of PolyBench/GPU-OpenACC**

William Killian <killian@udel.edu>
* Who annotated all test files to include a subset of OpenACC Directives

Scott Grauer-Gray <sgrauerg@udel.edu>
* Who provided 2D- and 3D-convolution kernel code

Louis-Noel Pouchet <pouchet@cse.ohio-state.edu>
* Who provided packaging and harmonization of all test files, the PolyBench infrastructure and machinery, and several reference C files.

Uday Bondugula <uday@csa.iisc.ernet.in>
* Who provided many of the original reference C files, including Fortran to C translation.

